Description: Next-Generation Integrated Offensive Environment for Kali Linux
 Apex Terminal synthesizes the high-performance rendering of Alacritty,
 the persistent session management of Tmux, and the modular microservice
 orchestration of modern C2 frameworks into a singular, cohesive,
 AI-augmented platform designed specifically for Kali Linux.
 .
 Features:
  - GPU-accelerated terminal rendering via wgpu/WebGPU
  - Native terminal multiplexer with client-server architecture
  - AI middleware with MCP protocol (local LLM inference via Ollama/Llama.cpp)
  - C2 framework connectors: Sliver (gRPC), Havoc (WebSocket),
    Mythic (GraphQL), Empire (REST API)
  - Shell stabilization engine with automatic PTY spawning
  - Tamper tracking and environment synchronization
  - Collaborative workspace management
  - Lua-based configuration engine
